{"tid":2430484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逾百人續湧法院 逼爆公眾席","createTime":"2021-03-03T03:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T03:32:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"367f7c207d38346044e43c8b7c428351efd36dda","tid":2430484,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/ZZB5NKPZDNC5DADKSUXEYBFXSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FZZB5NKPZDNC5DADKSUXEYBFXSY%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiutHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=df631cfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2FZZB5NKPZDNC5DADKSUXEYBFXSY%2F&h=c727428d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/ZZB5NKPZDNC5DADKSUXEYBFXSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n逾百人續湧法院 逼爆公眾席<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】 前日千人在西九裁判法院門外展示五一手勢為47名被告打氣後，昨日第二日聆訊情況稍為平靜。庭外聲援人士昨繼續穿黑衣，戴黃口罩聲援。由於前日輪候入庭人士眾多，不少市民專程提早前來排隊，164張公眾席籌瞬間派出，但仍有過百人等候後補位置。直至晚上在法院外聲援人潮不絕，包括示威常客王婆婆。有市民不滿鬧爆「法治已死」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：不人道聆訊 47子受折磨24小時<br />\n<br />\n清晨7時許，10多名身穿黑衣市民排隊等候進入公眾席，輪候人士隨後獲安排進入法院一樓輪候區，整個早上人潮絡繹不絕，幾乎迫爆輪候區。至早上11時，法庭在大門豎起水牌，提醒輪候人士164張公眾席籌已全數派出，但至中午12時仍有近百人輪候後補位置。不少人身穿黑衣、戴黃口罩表態，亦有女童用黃絲帶紥上孖辮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/12SK4LewyGsFow6c-WI_tcm1cyU=/1773x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YYIC4JOQIFH6RHWC5XG6VDXRQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F12SK4LewyGsFow6c-WI_tcm1cyU%3D%2F1773x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYYIC4JOQIFH6RHWC5XG6VDXRQI.jpg&h=7d1e3952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉慧卿（右二）昨排隊旁聽，直斥控方阻止保釋「好離譜」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉慧卿轟無程序公義<br />\n<br />\n示威常客王婆婆亦於下午舉起港英旗到場聲援，其間有警員手持限聚令告票，要求在場人士散開，否則將被票控。直至晚上，庭。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：張可森快做爸爸 梁晃維準備求婚  痛心又窩心 喜訊驅黑暗<br />\n<br />\n昨到場旁聽的民主黨國際事務委員會主席劉慧卿直斥控方阻止保釋「好離譜，都未定罪，就想囚禁人三個月」，令人感覺控方不理程序公義，只想盡快將47人還柙。<br />\n<br />\n另外續有市民到來聲援，杜先生指「警方查案，48小時後夠料就上庭，唔夠料就放人，𠵱家話要慢慢查，點解要還柙，呢個政權黐咗線。」林女士亦質疑法官的審判是否公平公正，還是否值得香港人信任，形容法庭。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eGnbyQhTPFrGrM0igtilsBnj1Xg=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/26RW6NLVUVGHRE4RNTH2ZY6PHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeGnbyQhTPFrGrM0igtilsBnj1Xg%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F26RW6NLVUVGHRE4RNTH2ZY6PHE.jpg&h=cf3f015e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黃耀明昨晚到法院為何桂藍作擔保。"},{"pid":"1b3acb2079b9be7ec801f72245eec22f62bc7cb6","tid":2430484,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T03:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}